author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the word "HELP" written into the ground with debris off a busy intersection in Los Angeles. Google Earth researchers found this a few days ago and the Internet has been rightfully worried. What's the truth behind this? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Disturbing Messages Found On Google Earth...
